<tr id="L339"><td><a href="#L339">339</a></td><td>MIRANDA:  But he is a Vulcan.</td></tr>

<tr id="L340"><td><a href="#L340">340</a></td><td>KIRK:  Only half. The other half is human. Far more human than you, apparently.</td></tr>

<tr id="L341"><td><a href="#L341">341</a></td><td>MIRANDA:  Face reality, Captain. His mind has gone down almost too far even for me to reach!</td></tr>

<tr id="L342"><td><a href="#L342">342</a></td><td>KIRK:  If you don't reach him soon, he'll die. But that's what you want, isn't it?</td></tr>

<tr id="L343"><td><a href="#L343">343</a></td><td>MIRANDA:  That's a lie!</td></tr>

<tr id="L344"><td><a href="#L344">344</a></td><td>KIRK:  Oh yes? You want him to die. What did you do to him on the Bridge? Did you make him forget to put the visor over his eyes?</td></tr>

<tr id="L345"><td><a href="#L345">345</a></td><td>MIRANDA:  You're insane!</td></tr>

<tr id="L346"><td><a href="#L346">346</a></td><td>KIRK:  Yes, you know your rival, don't you? You couldn't keep him from making a mind-link with Kollos, something you couldn't do yourself! With my words, I'll make you hear such ugliness as Spock saw when he looked at Kollos with his naked eyes! The ugliness is within you!</td></tr>

<tr id="L347"><td><a href="#L347">347</a></td><td>MIRANDA:  That's a lie! Liar!</td></tr>

<tr id="L348"><td><a href="#L348">348</a></td><td>KIRK:  Your desire to see Kollos is madness! You can never see him. Never. But Spock saw Kollos, and for that he must die.</td></tr>

<tr id="L349"><td><a href="#L349">349</a></td><td>MIRANDA:  Sadistic, filthy liar!</td></tr>

<tr id="L350"><td><a href="#L350">350</a></td><td>KIRK:  The smell of hatred, the stench of jealousy permeates you. Why don't you strangle him while he lies there?</td></tr>

<tr id="L351"><td><a href="#L351">351</a></td><td>MIRANDA:  Don't say anymore, please!</td></tr>

<tr id="L352"><td><a href="#L352">352</a></td><td>KIRK:  Kollos knows what's in your heart. You can lie to yourself, but you can't lie to Kollos.</td></tr>

<tr id="L353"><td><a href="#L353">353</a></td><td>MIRANDA:  Please go away!</td></tr>

<tr><td></td><td>LOCATION--Outside Sickbay</td></tr>
<tr id="L354"><td><a href="#L354">354</a></td><td>MCCOY:  What'd you say to her?</td></tr>

<tr id="L355"><td><a href="#L355">355</a></td><td>KIRK:  Maybe too much.</td></tr>

