<tr id="L357"><td><a href="#L357">357</a></td><td>KIRK:  You may be right, Bones. Maybe I shouldn't have gone in. She was blind, really blind. Really in the dark. And if he dies. If he dies, how do I know that I didn't kill him? How do I know that she can stand to hear the truth?</td></tr>

